      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 39 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 39 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蹇，利西南，不利東北；利見大人，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In (the state indicated by) Jian advantage will be found in the south-west, and the contrary in the north-east. It will be advantageous (also) to meet with the great man. (In these circumstances), with firmness and correctness, there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
